[I] A utility for creating X11 dialog boxes

[T] XDialog is a utility that allows you to show dialog boxes
[T] (containing questions or messages) in X11 (graphics mode)
[T] from shell scripts.

[U] http://xdialog.free.fr/

[A] Thierry Godefroy <xdialog@free.fr>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

